"title": "8311: morality, and redemption",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8311: morality, and redemption",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The morality which is appropriate for God's own people is expressed in the OT law, and in the person and teaching of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Relationship with God is expressed in moral terms</h2>\n<h3>In the moral standards God expects of his people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:44-Lev11:45\">LEV 11:44–11:45</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:48\">MAT 5:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:43-Matt5:44\">MAT 5:43–5:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27-Luke6:28\">LUK 6:27–6:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:35-Luke6:36\">LUK 6:35–6:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:31-Eph5:3\">EPH 4:31–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:15-1Pet1:16\">1PE 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/3John1:11\">3JN 1:11</a></p>\n<h3>In God's moral laws</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:4\">ISA 51:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:12\">ROM 7:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:1-Exod20:7\">EXO 20:1–20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:25\">DEU 6:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:137-Ps119:138\">PSA 119:137–119:138</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:19-Ps147:20\">PSA 147:19–147:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:18\">PRO 29:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:7\">ISA 51:7</a></p>\n<h3>In God's denunciation of immorality and religious hypocrisy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6-Amos2:7\">AMO 2:6–2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15-Isa1:23\">ISA 1:15–1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:21-Amos5:24\">AMO 5:21–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:8\">MIC 6:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5\">EPH 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5-Col3:7\">COL 3:5–3:7</a></p>\n<h3>In the life and teaching of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:17-Matt5:20\">MAT 5:17–5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:17-John1:18\">JHN 1:17–1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:19\">JHN 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a></p>\n<h2>The incentive for moral change lies in what God has done in redemption</h2>\n<h3>In the OT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:17-Deut24:18\">DEU 24:17–24:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13-Lev19:18\">LEV 19:13–19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:35-Lev19:36\">LEV 19:35–19:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut15:12-Deut15:15\">DEU 15:12–15:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut24:21-Deut24:22\">DEU 24:21–24:22</a></p>\n<h3>In the NT</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:19-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:19–6:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a></p>\n<h2>Moral change brought about by God's work of renewal</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26-Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:26–36:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:9–6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3-Rom8:4\">ROM 8:3–8:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11-Rom8:14\">ROM 8:11–8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19-Gal5:24\">GAL 5:19–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:22-Eph4:24\">EPH 4:22–4:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:12-Phil2:13\">PHP 2:12–2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:8-Col3:12\">COL 3:8–3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:10\">HEB 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33\">JER 31:33</a></p>",
